Functional Requirements:
-User login
-User can enter in money spent, to keep track of expenditures
-User can enters amounts to allocate budget to different categories.
-User can add or modify categories
-user can modify and delete existing transactions
-user can view all past and present transactions.
-entries should contain, amount, date, category, and description.
-user can have different bank accounts that money is being put into or used from
	- i.e pay utility bill from citi bank acc.
-Can have multiple budgets (Ledgers)


Non-Functional Requirements:
-There should be a difference between inflow and outflow of money
-Everything should be done on 1 page.

Tkinter version will be a YNAB4 open source alternative
Django version will be a web app open alternative.
